# 🐍 Python (Backend)
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/env/
**/ENV/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/

# 🔐 Secrets & Local Configuration
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local
**/*.env

# 🎨 IDEs & OS Configuration
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.swp


**/logs/
